                          <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">1</label>
                          <para xml:lang="en-NZ">
                            <text>Every annual and half-year financial statement shall be accompanied by a statement of responsibility signed by the Minister, any other Minister designated by the Prime Minister for either or both of the purposes of <citation jurisdiction="nz">paragraphs (a) and (d) of subsection (2)</citation>, and the Secretary.</text>
                          </para>
